OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly dry and bright start.
OL,6,FShowery outbreaks of rain will then
OL,7,Fdevelop during the morning and move
OL,8,Feast through the afternoon. Rather
OL,9,Fbreezy around coasts. Warmer than
OL,10,Fyesterday.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThere will be a mixture of
OL,13,Fclear intervals and showers, these
OL,14,Fmore frequent over Moray in the
OL,15,Fevening and early night.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FAnother mixed day with some
OL,18,Fbrighter spells but also some showers,
OL,19,Fwhich may become slow moving and bring
OL,20,Fsome longer spells of rain to
OL,21,FAberdeenshire later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
