OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FSaturday starting dry before cloud and
OL,7,Frain push up into Aberdeenshire for a
OL,8,Fwhile. Dry start Sunday then rain
OL,9,Fspreading from northwest, lasting into
OL,10,FMonday before it brightens up later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
